submittedFiles.workflow:
version 1.0

import "./tasks/ReferencePanelQc.wdl" as qc
import "./tasks/BcftoolsCall.wdl" as bcftools
import "./tasks/Glimpse.wdl" as glimpse
import "./tasks/TargetPanelQc.wdl" as depth_qc

workflow GlimpsePipeline {
    input {
        File fasta_reference
        Array[SampleAlignment] samples
        Array[String] chromosomes
        Array[File] chromosome_maps
        Map[String, File] reference_panel
        String glimpse_container
        String gatk_container
        Int min_depth
        Boolean? impute_reference_only_sites
        Int window_size
        Int buffer_size
    }

    Boolean impute_ref_only = select_first([impute_reference_only_sites, false])

    call qc.ReferencePanelQc {
        input:
            chromosomes=chromosomes,
            reference_panel=reference_panel
    }

    call bcftools.BcftoolsToVCFs {
        input:
            fasta_reference=fasta_reference,
            samples=samples,
            chromosomes=ReferencePanelQc.chromosomes_list,
            reference_panel=ReferencePanelQc.vcfs,
            reference_panel_index=ReferencePanelQc.vcfs_index,
            min_depth=min_depth
    }

    call depth_qc.DepthDistributionOfCoveredSites {
        input:
            cohort_vcf=BcftoolsToVCFs.ngs_vcf,
            cohort_vcf_index=BcftoolsToVCFs.ngs_vcf_index,
            min_depth=min_depth
    }

    call glimpse.GlimpseImputation {
        input:
            target_population_vcf=BcftoolsToVCFs.ngs_vcf,
            target_population_vcf_index=BcftoolsToVCFs.ngs_vcf_index,
            glimpse_container=glimpse_container,
            gatk_container=gatk_container,
            chromosomes=ReferencePanelQc.chromosomes_list,
            chromosome_maps=chromosome_maps,
            hq_reference_panel=ReferencePanelQc.vcfs,
            hq_reference_panel_idx=ReferencePanelQc.vcfs_index,
            impute_reference_only_sites=impute_ref_only,
            window_size=window_size,
            buffer_size=buffer_size
    }
}
